      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This car has been such a joy to own and is still in really solid shape. It runs beautifully and has plenty of life left in it for your daily commutes or fun weekend road trips! I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a good home. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to help you get behind the wheel of this beauty!",
