    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for superior longitudinal traction. Key preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and a reinforced rear subframe to maintain structural rigidity under lateral load. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative steering feel synonymous with the chassis. Finished in Carbon Black, this vehicle represents a well-maintained entry into M-division performance, balanced for both spirited canyon carving and reliable touring.",
