    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2020 Lexus RX 350 offers a perfect blend of luxury and long-term dependability. The exterior paint retains a brilliant luster, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical signs of careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of premium materials; the leather seats are in great shape, showing only light creasing on the driver's side bolster. All electronics, from the heated steering wheel to the intuitive infotainment system, operate perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly, backed by a complete service history. The tires have significant tread remaining, and the brake feel is firm and responsive. This is a well-cared-for vehicle that delivers a quiet, composed ride without the 'new car' price tag.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
